-- Deutsche Bank Hires Henry Cai as Chairman of Corporate Finance in Asia
-- Bei Hu
-- 2010-07-18T10:14:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-18/deutsche-bank-hires-henry-cai-as-chairman-of-corporate-finance-in-asia.html

          
          
             Deutsche Bank AG  hired  Henry Cai 
from UBS AG as chairman of corporate finance in Asia, it said in
an e-mailed statement today.  
 Cai, whose appointment will begin in Hong Kong on Oct. 4,
will also be chairman of the German lender’s corporate and
investment bank in China, the statement said. He will report to
 Robert Rankin , Deutsche Bank’s chief executive officer in the
Asia-Pacific region, it added.  
 Cai was most recently Asia chairman of investment banking
at UBS AG, the statement said.  
